Class ImmutableProvider<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.Observable
      • com.defano.jmonet.model.ImmutableProvider<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of value being provided.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Observer
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Provider

    public class ImmutableProvider<T>
extends Observable
implements Observer
    Provides an Observable interface to a variable whose value may change over time, but whose value cannot be changed by this provider.
